Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.81,0:00:13.36,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten deň, keď brat odišiel, všetko bolo šedé...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:18.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dokonca aj slnko a vlny.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.69,0:00:23.30,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale teraz je to iné...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.30,0:00:30.21,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Svetlo, ktoré dopadá, je teraz svetlo nenávisti, ktoré nesmie zhasnúť.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.21,0:00:33.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat, si takto šťastný?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:38.95,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je ten pravý čas...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.95,0:00:41.72,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sirius, náš najnovší Anjel...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:49.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoj príchod do Atlandie zmenil pomer mýtickej sily na svete.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:51.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Strom života zrodil
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.29,0:00:55.73,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,zberača, ako krásny padajúci sneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.73,0:00:59.84,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Začal klesať na zem bezkrídlych.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.84,0:01:07.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz, môžeme ostať v Atlandii, kým pozbiera ich Pranu...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.71,0:01:12.94,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Môže priniesť ešte väčšiu slávu Atlandii...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.99,0:01:23.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sneh zberača, ktorý dokáže zničiť svet, padá z Atlandie...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.43,0:01:25.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Z Atlandie?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.70,0:01:37.54,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}V čase, v čase neznámom, ideme s istotou.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.72,0:01:54.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Pod vysvieteným kopcom sme si vyznali počiatok
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.39,0:01:57.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Kvôli tebe a aj sebe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.39,0:01:59.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Prehľadávam, prehľadávam.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.73,0:02:08.74,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Po tisícročiach osamelosti som sa stretla s tvojim uhrančivým pohľadom
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.74,0:02:10.07,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Prehľadávam, prehľadávam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.07,0:02:14.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Chcem byť spojená!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:19.75,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Je to príjemný pocit vzrušenia!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.75,0:02:25.09,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Je to, ako keby sa táto sila zrodila z morskej peny!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.09,0:02:31.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}V čase, v čase neznámom, ideme s istotou.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.43,0:02:34.10,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Tieto slzy dojatia, to rozhodne nie je žiaden sen,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.10,0:02:36.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}toto je útek za láskou.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.43,0:02:39.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Všetko čo máme sú naše srdcia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:42.10,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Naše nádeje sú v nekonečnej čiernej diere.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.10,0:02:48.13,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,200)}Chcem, aby sme boli spojení, a to naveky.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:03.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Podpriestorové portály sa objavili po celom svete!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:05.99,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čísla stále narastajú!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:08.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je ich približne 12.000!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:20.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Mýtická beštia ako sneh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:24.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Preto neznášam veci, ktoré padajú z neba!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.71,0:03:29.48,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,V mojom domove nikdy nesnežilo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:31.22,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale teraz...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.22,0:03:33.62,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pierre...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.62,0:03:36.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia! Čo robíš?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.39,0:03:42.23,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Môže nás zradiť ako Sirius!?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.23,0:03:46.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Preto som bol proti pilotom s krvou Ťieňových Anjelov!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:49.30,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo hovoríš?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:52.94,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Má v úmysle ho priviesť späť...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:55.61,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nedokážem pochopiť tvoje zámery, brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:58.91,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A čo robíš je neodpustitelné...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.91,0:04:02.51,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale ja... ja...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.29,0:04:08.19,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:23.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prana z celého sveta je prenášaná sem vďaka mýtickej beštii
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:28.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,ako výživu pre strom života, aby dosiahol až do neba.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:35.98,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hlavné mesto Anjelov sa znovu zrodí.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:39.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako dlho som čakal na túto chvíľu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:48.56,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď sa Slnečné Krídlo skutočne prebudí, strom života zrodí ovocie
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:52.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,a dá život novému svetu Anjelov...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.47,0:04:57.31,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pohnime si.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:59.84,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz je čas na opaľovanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.84,0:05:04.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak to premeškáme, tak kvety zvädnú a zomrú.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:07.52,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.52,0:05:10.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Máš zakázaný vstup na palubu Vectora, až do odvolania.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:15.86,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ešte nie si zbavená podozrenia z pokusu o útek do Atlandie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.86,0:05:20.45,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia... Budeš v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:28.87,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten, na ktorého čaká, príde z Neba ako sneh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.87,0:05:33.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Strom, ktorý je zdrojom obrovského nešťastia bude čoskoro prinášať ovocie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:35.74,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten, na ktorého čaká?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:37.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemyslíš...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:39.28,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sirius?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:40.62,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Neviem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.62,0:05:45.21,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Hovorím, že hlas prichádza z tadiaľ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:53.09,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepáč, že to poviem... Zabudni na neho.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.09,0:05:57.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zabudnúť na neho?! Je to môj jediný brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.70,0:05:59.27,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale aj keď brat môže mať niečo spoločné s tým,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:02.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,čo sa deje na svete...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.48,0:06:10.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To nie je on...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.85,0:06:13.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toma a jeho banda sú zlí!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:15.42,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Takýmto spôsobom nebudeš môcť spraviť nič!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:18.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Buď silná! Ver!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.59,0:06:32.10,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako to bolo pred 12.000 rokmi, keď raj padol,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:35.07,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,pripravujeme sa na konečnú bitku.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:41.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Najblišie budú zničení ľudia alebo Ťieňoví Anjely?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:47.25,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Príjmeme osud alebo my, ako ľudstvo, budeme bojovať?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:52.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Spýtajte sa samy seba. Nech neľutujete!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.26,0:07:06.20,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozorujte, pán Fudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:09.84,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Masovú výrobu Útočného Aquariona
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:12.07,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,vynájdeného spoločne medzi armádou a Deavou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:16.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto telo, ozbrojené PSG kvantovými zbraňami,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:22.52,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,zničia bariéru Atlandie, o ktorej si mysleli, že je nezničiteľná...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.52,0:07:26.49,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakoniec sa okrídlený naučia...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:32.13,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,aké márne sú krídla tvárou v tvár našej inteligencii.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:37.13,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Za týmto účelom, dáta a vzorky Elementov Deavy boli veľmi užitočné
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.13,0:07:43.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,na pochopenie a klonovanie sily pierok Ťieňových Anjelov.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.09,0:08:00.76,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jedzte kým môžete...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:03.72,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak budete jesť, tak budete môcť lietať. Môžete byť silný.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:25.44,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Chytaj.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.08,0:08:30.88,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jedz.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.37,0:08:52.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Závidím vtákom...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:09:00.24,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Priala by som si lietať medzi nebom a zemou...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:11.72,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tu je viac. Jedz, koľko len chceš.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:21.07,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jedz, jedz a jedz ako šialená.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:26.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Potom budeš môcť lietať. Staneš sa silnou.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:29.81,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,My dokážeme lietať... Ty a ja.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:32.28,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Teraz sa nemôžeme pozrieť na nikoho...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.28,0:09:36.27,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale pre tú srandu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:47.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Inštruktorka, kde sú všetci?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:51.13,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Trávia čas s tými, ktorých milujú?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:53.84,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To je ten čas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.84,0:09:58.04,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Som šťastlivec! Tak som ostal sám s tebou, Sophia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:09:59.11,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:01.41,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemá zmysel teraz váhať!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:04.28,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Žijem svoj život tak, ako keby mal byť posledný, tak...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:06.44,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Práve teraz je to v poriadku!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:14.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem, aby si žil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:20.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A všetci.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.74,0:10:36.48,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pierre...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:39.21,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Upiekla som ovocný koláč...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.21,0:10:42.35,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je plný vitamínov... Máš nejaký?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:44.62,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:46.61,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sestra...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.44,0:11:02.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.04,0:11:07.48,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pred 12.000 rokmi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.48,0:11:13.11,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Myslíš si, že sme sa takto spolu prechádzali?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.35,0:11:18.11,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kto vie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:26.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale cítim, ako keby som ťa poznal celú večnosť...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:33.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Podľa tvojej vône...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.37,0:11:35.17,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:06.73,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kam mohla zmiznúť Tsugumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.73,0:12:09.50,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Našiel som pre ňu úžasné náradie...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:13.34,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sempai, pre vás.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:16.07,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem, Tsugumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.08,0:12:22.45,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Šťastie je pominuteľné...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:26.15,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale nešťastie nikdy neskončí.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.15,0:12:29.09,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To nie je tak, Sempai! Som s vami!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.09,0:12:30.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.33,0:12:35.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo vás sem privádza?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:39.73,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Počuli sme, že konečá bitka sa blíži...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:42.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto je od nás.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:48.74,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,V reči kvetov to znamená "večné šťastie."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.61,0:12:51.98,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Šťastie...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:55.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem, všetkým...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.53,0:13:10.53,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetci zomrieme kvôli bratovi a jemu podobným?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.53,0:13:13.83,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To sa nestane! My ich zastavíme!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:20.34,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ako som povedal... budeme lietať. V Aquarionovi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.34,0:13:23.91,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale... určite sa vrátime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.91,0:13:26.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nechcem, aby si mi znova ušiel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:31.11,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sľúb mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:42.99,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Známa vôňa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.77,0:13:47.23,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Známy zvuk...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:05.75,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo sa deje?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.75,0:14:07.62,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozri sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:14.13,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je tu... Brat je tu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:16.23,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brat je blízko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.23,0:14:18.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo? Kde?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:20.63,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kde je?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:25.27,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Videla si ho?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.28,0:14:31.87,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:36.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:42.55,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:55.46,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:03.78,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.78,0:15:05.30,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sempai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:12.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ach, nie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.09,0:15:17.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi, ideme!\NÁno!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.87,0:15:27.42,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sempai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.18,0:15:35.74,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Toto sa nemôže diať!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:38.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dostali sa cez konečnú bariéru Deavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:40.91,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je iba otázkou času, kým sa sem dostanú!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:43.52,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Chloe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.52,0:15:45.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sestra!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.85,0:15:47.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Chloe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:50.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakra... sakra... sakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:55.63,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Si v poriadku, Chloe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:58.93,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zjedz ten koláč, dobre?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:16:03.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nebuď smiešna! Zjeme ho spolu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.18,0:16:10.38,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Chloe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:12.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Chloe!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:17.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Bol tu. Sirius bol tu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:19.62,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:21.92,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten zradca?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:25.89,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia... zobral Silviu so sebou...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.89,0:16:28.06,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je to pravda?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.06,0:16:30.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jej vôňa zmizla...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.30,0:16:37.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetci sú v poriadku?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:39.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerome! Tvoje rozkazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.77,0:16:41.78,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ja, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:45.28,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerome, kým sa veliteľ Fudo vráti zo základne,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.28,0:16:48.44,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,velíš!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:56.36,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Táto informácia je prísne tajná.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.36,0:16:59.16,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Práve teraz sú nasadené vojenské ničiace jednotky.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:00.26,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.26,0:17:03.80,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Povedal som, že to vyhladí Atlandiu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:05.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.37,0:17:08.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak to spravia, čo sa stane Silvii?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:11.27,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Uniesli ju tam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.27,0:17:14.31,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžeš ich zastaviť?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.31,0:17:16.21,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To je asi márne.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.21,0:17:17.18,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:19.95,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,To preto bude Deava...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.95,0:17:22.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,...pracovať samostatne!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.32,0:17:24.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:28.56,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:29.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.32,0:17:30.02,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:31.59,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, pane!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.59,0:17:32.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Áno, pane!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.79,0:17:36.56,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Mechanický Anjel Aquarion! Ihneď choďte!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.56,0:17:37.16,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Idem!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:38.65,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Rozkaz!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.67,0:17:47.71,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Jerome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:50.75,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideme!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:54.91,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zabijácky úder Mugen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.59,0:18:06.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ich citlivosť Gattai je...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.79,0:18:10.70,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aura Vectoru Sol, Apolla, klesá!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.70,0:18:12.60,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aká silná môže byť tá bariéra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:16.64,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Poškodenie sa zvyšuje na pranom rameni Vectora Luna, Reiky!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:18.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zo všetkých nešťastných čias...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.37,0:18:21.04,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Zlyháme kvôli mne?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.04,0:18:23.91,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, Sempai, ste úžasná!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:27.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Prosím! Nechajte ma byť hlavou!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.05,0:18:28.58,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Chceš byť hlavou?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:31.32,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemôžem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:36.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nechcem byť stále niekym ochraňovaná!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.66,0:18:41.03,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem vás všetkých ochrániť!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:44.33,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.33,0:18:46.80,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.80,0:18:49.37,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dobre! Tak to sprav!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.37,0:18:51.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nenshin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.14,0:18:52.17,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:53.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Gattai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:55.91,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sempai!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.91,0:18:58.11,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideš! Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.38,0:19:04.08,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je to za pocit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.08,0:19:06.75,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi, práve si...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.39,0:19:10.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Blaho!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:14.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion Anjel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:21.44,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.44,0:19:23.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:25.07,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumin srdečný rytmus narastá!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.07,0:19:27.07,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aury síl idú do kritických hodnôt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:30.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi! Nepreháňaj to!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:33.98,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie, teraz je na čase, aby sa postarala o stenu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:35.42,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Veliteľ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:38.05,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi teraz nie je sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.05,0:19:39.15,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.15,0:19:40.42,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Počujem to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.42,0:19:41.99,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Rena?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:44.72,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,...rytmus vášnivého srdca.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.23,0:19:50.83,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi... Drž sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.83,0:19:53.00,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem, Jun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:53.83,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:55.97,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.97,0:19:59.51,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ďakujem... všetkým!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:01.78,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:05.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Chcem, aby ste vedeli, Sempai...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.85,0:20:10.85,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Je jedno čo sa stane,nikdy sa nevzdáte a ostanete verná...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:13.29,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Preto vás milujem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:15.39,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.39,0:20:18.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,A tiež milujem každého v Deave...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.80,0:20:25.89,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nie je obmedzené, ako dokážete milovať!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.64,0:20:35.91,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Bolesť, smútok, všetko, čo robí človeka...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.91,0:20:40.61,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Všetko to milujem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:49.66,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(323,174)}"Nekonečné svetlo vybuchujúcej lásky"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:06.74,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Atlandia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:09.14,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:13.75,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Dostala sa cez stenu do neba, do ktorého som nemohol preniknúť päsťou...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:15.25,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,...svetlom z jej srdca.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.25,0:21:17.79,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi! Buď silná.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.79,0:21:18.82,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Sempai...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:19.82,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.82,0:21:25.76,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Budem v poriadku... Nedovolím, aby vaše nešťastie postihlo ešte niekoho...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:27.56,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:33.87,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Táto vec ma neporazí!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:35.80,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Reika!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.80,0:21:38.74,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideme, Apollo. Pre Tsugumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.74,0:21:40.40,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Som s tebou!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.69,0:21:59.69,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Neverím tomu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.69,0:22:01.93,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vojenské Vectory!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.93,0:22:06.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Aké hnusné! Využili nás?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.90,0:22:09.43,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Vráťte sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.86,0:23:46.47,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Brány osudu boli otvorené.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.47,0:23:49.90,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Kto bude vyvolený? Ľudia? Alebo Ťieňoví Anjely?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.90,0:23:52.87,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Nabudúce v Aquarionovi: "Konečný boj! Atlandia"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.87,0:23:53.77,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Apollo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.77,0:23:55.01,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Silvia!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:23:57.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,Pozerajte, všetci.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:23:59.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(405,400)}"Konečný boj! Atlandia"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.57,0:24:01.57,Aquarion,,0000,0000,0000,,
